| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4750 — Recovery Inhibition (everest)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7e4f03e4-7e9c-5fcb-a120-a98c3d47f146"
